// Gamelan Pelog — 7-note Javanese scale
// nem barang bem gulu lima enam pitu
// Non-equal intervals, metallic resonance

@core
@controls
@alphabet.gamelan_pelog:browser
@mm:55

S -> Patutan Phrase End

Patutan -> nem barang bem gulu lima enam pitu (wave:square, vel:75)
Phrase -> pitu _ enam lima _ gulu bem _ barang nem _
End -> nem _ _ _ _ _ (vel:55)
